dia.org/resource/Jackie_Young_(basketball)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Young_(basketball)\"}, {\"begin\": 1195, \"end\": 1207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_Gray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chelsea Gray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_Gray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_Gray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been something that I have wanted to do ever since I was a little girl,\\\" Ionescu said.\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1308, \"end\": 1315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabrina_Ionescu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6225079073880884e-39, \"text\": \"Ionescu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabrina_Ionescu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabrina_Ionescu\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I understand that I would be able to have the opportunity to go out and compete with the best in the world, go out there, and fight for another gold medal.\\\"\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1479, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00c2  Ionescu has helped the Liberty to an impressive 10-2 record on the season and are in second place in league standings.\\u00c2\\u00a0Ionescu recently made WNBA history as the fastest player to reach 300 three-pointers in a career.\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1700, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1506, \"end\": 1513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberty_Flames_football\", \"score\": 0.6473600878932014, \"rank\": 0.5432501292740677, \"text\": \"Liberty\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberty_Flames_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberty_Flames_football\"}, {\"begin\": 1625, \"end\": 1629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.168618751029451e-16, \"text\": \"WNBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And now Ionescu will take her talents on an international stage to the 2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1710, \"end\": 1717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabrina_Ionescu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6225079073880884e-39, \"text\": \"Ionescu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabrina_Ionescu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabrina_Ionescu\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1821, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please wait while we load personalized content recommendations  Bri Amaranthus is an Emmy-winning sports reporter with over 12 years of experience in television, radio, podcasting, and digital sports journalism.\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 2033, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She has been with Sports Illustrated for four years, providing breaking news, exclusive interviews, and analysis on the NFL, college sports, and the NBA.\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2187, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2052, \"end\": 2070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.527926804929103e-20, \"text\": \"Sports Illustrated\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\"}, {\"begin\": 2154, \"end\": 2157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.9998798294333398, \"rank\": 5.758168301424979e-05, \"text\": \"NFL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Na